-395; Guinée, J.B., Huppes, G., Heijungs, R., (2001) Environ. Manag. Health, 12, pp. 301-311; Huijbregts, M.A.J., Seppälä, J., (2001) Int. J. Life Cycle Assess., 6, pp. 339-343; Cano-Ruiz, J.A., (2000) Decision Support Tools for Environmentally Conscious Chemical Process Design, pp. 150-156. , Thesis, MIT, Cambridge, MA; (1994) Energy Performance of Dwellings and Residential Buildings - Determination Method (in Dutch), , Dutch Normalisation Institute: Delft; (1995) Energy Performance of Dwellings and Residential Buildings - Examples (in Dutch), , Dutch Normalisation Institute: Delft; Mak, J.P., Anink, D.A., Kortman, L.G.M., Ewijk, H.A.L., (1996) Ecoquantum - Final Report (in Dutch), , W/E Adviseurs: Gouda; Bennett, D.H., Scheringer, M., McKone, T.E., Hungelbühler, K., (2001) Environ. Sci. Technol., 35, pp. 1181-1189; Slob, W., (1994) Risk Anal., 14, pp. 571-576; MacLeod, M., Fraser, A.J., Mackay, D., (2002) Environ. Toxicol. Chem., 21, pp. 700-709; Hertwich, E.G., McKone, T.E., Pease, W.S., (1999) Risk Anal., 19, pp. 1193-1204; McKone, T.E., (1996) Relat. Eng. Syst. Saf., 54, pp. 165-181; McKone, T.E., Ryan, P.B., (1989) Environ. Sci. Technol., 23, pp. 1154-1163; Rabl, A., Spadaro, J.V., (1999) Environ. Int., 25, pp. 29-46; Jager, T., Vermeire, T.G., Rikken, M.G.J., Van der Poel, P., (2001) Chemosphere, 43, pp. 257-264; Wayne, R.O., (1990) J. Air Waste Manage. Assoc., 40, pp. 1378-1383; Kortman, J.G.M., Eggels, P.G., Huppes, G., Van Oers, L., Lindeijer, E.W., Van der Ven, E.L., Guinée, J.B., (1996) Assessment of the Environmental Impacts of Recycling of Long Life Products at the End-of-Life Stage (in Dutch), , Report 96.155x; RIZA: Lelystad; Ekvall, T., Tillman, A.-M., (1997) Int. J. Life Cycle Assess., 2, pp. 155-162; Finnveden, G., (1999) Resour. Conserv. Recycl., 26, pp. 173-187; Ramaswamy, V., Boucher, O., Haigh, J., Hauglustaine, D., Haywood, J., Myhre, G., Nakajima, T., Solomon, S., Radiative forcing of climate change (2001) Climate Change 2001: The Scientific